OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776363050
OL,3,CBus drivers settle pay dispute with
OL,4,CIsle of Man Government
OL,6,FBus drivers on the Isle of Man have
OL,7,Fvoted to accept a pay offer from the
OL,8,Fgovernment, after a long-running
OL,9,Fdispute over pay and working
OL,10,Fconditions.
OL,12,FUnite the Union and the Department of
OL,13,FInfrastructure confirmed that the
OL,14,Findustrial dispute involving Bus
OL,15,FVannin drivers has now been resolved
OL,16,Ffollowing a ballot of Unite the Union
OL,17,Fmembers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
