FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776363050
OL,3,CBus drivers settle pay dispute with
OL,4,CIsle of Man Government
OL,6,FThey say the agreement 'secures an
OL,7,Fimproved pay position for drivers and
OL,8,Fprovides a basis for stability going
OL,9,Fforward'.
OL,11,FFive rounds of strike action took
OL,12,Fplace between February and March,
OL,13,Fleaving the buses running on a reduced
OL,14,Fservice while negotiations continued.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776363050
OL,3,CBus drivers settle pay dispute with
OL,4,CIsle of Man Government
OL,6,FDebbie Halsall, Head of Unite in the
OL,7,FIsle of Man, said: "This outcome
OL,8,Freflects the strength of feeling from
OL,9,Four members and delivers a clear
OL,10,Fimprovement on pay. Whilst for some
OL,11,Fthis is a bittersweet moment, it is
OL,12,Fimportant this now provides a stable
OL,13,Ffooting to move forward."
OL,15,FInfrastructure Minister Tim Crookall
OL,16,FMHK said: "I welcome resolution of the
OL,17,Fdispute and the opportunities it
OL,18,Foffers for everyone at bus vannin and
OL,19,Fthe travelling public."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
